        "heading": "Roasting consistently great coffee from farms we actually visit. Just like Mike taught us.",
        "body": "<p>PCR was built on a simple idea: that great coffee starts long before the roaster. It starts at the farm. Dave learned that firsthand in the early 2010s, when he walked into Mike's Highway 9 coffee shop and met someone who took the whole chain — seed to cup — seriously. The two became fast friends, then business partners, buying a roaster together and chasing the kind of coffee that can change your life.</p><p>We lost Mike unexpectedly in 2025. His passion for the craft lives on in every roast we pull, and his memory has deepened our ties to the Pacific Coast recovery community — a cause close to Dave's heart.</p><p><strong>10% of every bag of Mike's Blend goes straight to supporting Santa Cruz County recovery programs.</strong></p>",
